 &lt;p&gt;Rui Santos questiona como &#xe9; que o Benfica n&#xe3;o aproveitou o deslize do Sporting ap&#xf3;s a sa&#xed;da de Amorim.&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;No programa desta noite o comentador da CNN responde &#xe0;s seguintes quest&#xf5;es do p&#xfa;blico:&lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;- Cr&#xea; que Bruno Lage &#xe9; um treinador que tem mesmo estofo para treinar o Benfica?&amp;#xa0;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;- Bruno Lage j&#xe1; perdeu o balne&#xe1;rio? Onde est&#xe1; o discurso unificador quando chegou? N&#xe3;o andou Bruno Lage a vender uma imagem ao p&#xfa;blico e ao balne&#xe1;rio que n&#xe3;o &#xe9; verdadeira?&amp;#xa0;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt; &amp;#xa0;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;-Por que motivo tudo &#xb4;permitido a Di Mar&#xed;a e n&#xe3;o h&#xe1; coragem de lhe mostrarem um vermelho? &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p class=&quot;Corpo&quot; style=&quot;border:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;-&amp;#xa0;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;H&#xe1; uma ideia de falta de garra no futebol do Benfica. &#xc9; real? Como se explica? @djdavod1_oficial&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p class=&quot;Corpo&quot; style=&quot;border:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt; Como avalia Bruno Lage como treinador? E a comunica&#xe7;&#xe3;o: perdeu-se?@diogobermejo e @sergiocarreirada&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p class=&quot;Corpo&quot; style=&quot;border:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt&quot;&gt;- &#xc9; a altura certa para come&#xe7;ar a pensar em dispensar Otamendi e Di Maria? @mpaulino72&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
